    <ul>
        <li>Fixed page bouncing on chrome when the download bar is at the bottom.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p class="feature">Safari</p>
    <ul>
        
        <li>Scroll buttons now work on Safari.</li>
        <li>Fixed text-size on Safari</li>
    </ul>
    


    <h3>Current Issues</h3>
    <p class="feature">Programs</p>
    <ul>
        <li>There is no instant feedback when importing a program.</li>
        <li>There is no instant feedback when modifying competency elements.</li>
    </ul>



    



