<div class="collapse" aria-expanded="true" id="collapse226">

    <h3>Highlights</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Redesign of the implementation of general education</li>
        <li>Various enhancements</li>
        <li>Various bug fixes (resolved Issues)</li>
