    <ul>
        <li>Password validation is consistent across entire system.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="feature">Back button fully functional</p>
    <ul>
        <li>The back button is now fully functional.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Current Issues</h3>
    <p class="feature">Programs</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Modified programs remain active rather than being deactivated and a modified copy being created and activated.</li>
        <li>Inactive programs can be fully modified.</li>
        <li>There is no instant feedback when importing a program.</li>
        <li>There is no instant feedback when modifying competency elements.</li>
    </ul>

