        <li>Scroll buttons do not work on Safari.</li>
        <li>Login fields on Safari mobile are very small.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="feature">Documents</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Documents can be uploaded to an archived Candidate.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="feature">Notifications</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Candidate does not receive email notifying them that a document was uploaded to their profile.</li>
        <li>RAC Advisor home has an empty notification.</li>
    </ul>

